collectionMetadata.name: Sample Household Survey: HDB Resident Population by Geographical Distribution
collectionMetadata.description:
Data is derived from the Sample Household Survey (SHS) which is conducted once every 5 years. HDB resident population refers to Singapore citizens and Singapore permanent residents (SPRs) residing in HDB flats. They include owners/co-owners, HDB rental tenants and occupiers.

Figures may not add to 10% due to rounding.
